item.title: ‘The Paper’ Gets NBC Run, Cheerleading Comedy ‘Stumble’ Joins Fall Schedule
item.description: The two shows fill in the last empty spots on the network’s primetime lineup; the Tracy Morgan-led ‘Fall and Rise of Reggie Dinkins’ goes to midseason.
